snippet.textDisplay:
idk why i analyze this shi im sad now, all of the kisses have god tier soundtrack but there's differences in both cases:

(Blonde Blazer) BB or mandy second kiss scene body lenguage is kinda off? (ep 4) she grabs roberts neck and back head something like holding into him, is seems like a peacefull kiss stable and very relaxed taking breaks between them, the camera starts to spins around them like a perfect kiss or couple taked out of a fantasy, at the end mandy is the only person holding while robert just hold her waist of the angle off the camera and opens his eyes and mandy goes back where she was standing, Mandy finale kiss seems peacefull as well very paused and the camera favorates mandy an her expresions like happy and satisfied the kiss while she holds the not damage ear part of him ends with her and robert looking at the sky very peacefull and chill like looking into a future blind trust maybe, most of the scenes with blonde blazer u can see there's lack of eye contact but the dance scene, cuz the idea of the romance with her is love at first sight, Robert seems calm and with a slight smile in his face in the dance scene but i can notice that there's a lack of bright in his eyes on every scene in romance blazer and seems a little off but might be the angle

(Invisigal) Visi or Courtney first kiss scene will always be a shock for robert eyes wide open the first moment is kinda weird ngl, Visi stoles the first kiss going invisible cuz maybe she isn't sure if he will accept her feelings so she at least has that taste if he decides to reject her, she steps back and makes direct eye contact with robert and robert recives the kiss, leaning in is the way to go Robert body lenguage is taking Visi's face, and Visi body lenguage is taking Robert's face to be more especific where his damaged ear is, Visi in this scene first moment she is equal on height but then she is very small, vulnerable her real face or side and robert embraces her with her body, next angle is from above where both characters can be seen very small and both are trying to grip and get closer, next shot is a close one where both are taking eachother, very equal, there's no breaks in the kiss, very passionate, chaotic with eyes closed that reflect a lot of emotions (pain, calm, desesperation, love and a lot more) this end with Robert touching Visi's waist when she disapears might be cuz she is fragile and scared in that moment.

There's always eye contact between this two and it's very weird seeing them break this eye contact lit the eyes speak for them.

There's a lot more but dayum i got tired ngl
